org.universAAL.middleware.interfaces.configuration.configurationDefinitionTypes

Interface DynamicDescribedEntity


  • public interface DynamicDescribedEntity
    Additonally to DescribedEntities, this interfaced may be added. This should only be done for configurations that may change locally, ie not only through ConfigurableModule.configurationChanged(Scope, Object).
    when the listener is called ConfigurableModule.configurationChanged(Scope, Object) will be called, and local and remote ConfigurationEditors will be notified.
    Author:
    amedrano
